    <texts>
      <txt a="X" c="X" e="-3" pt="1">How can you best protect yourself against the most common injuries: sprains or cuts in hands, arms or fingers?</txt>
      <txt crct="4" c="X">By avoiding operations and jobs that can cause such accidents</txt>
      <txt crct="38" c="X">By using gloves when practical, and being observant of the risk</txt>
      <txt crct="26" c="X">By never touching anything with your hands and always using some kind of tool</txt>
      <txt crct="15" c="X">It depends on the work requirement.</txt>
    </texts>
